        "把知识库分享给某人/给某人加入知识库/邀请进知识库",
        "查看具体命令的完整参数说明"
      ],
      "effect": "write",
      "effect_source": "command-verb",
      "examples": [
        "dws wiki member add --help",
        "dws wiki member add --workspace \u003cWS_ID\u003e --users uid1 --role READER"
